Package: superheat
Type: Package
Title: A graphical method for graphically exploring datasets and model
    assessment
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Rebecca", "Barter", email = "rebeccabarter@berkeley.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package which can be used to explore datasets and assess
    the adequacy of model fits using supervised heatmaps. The plot is highly
    customizable and has a large number of aesthetic options.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
License: CC0
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    dplyr (>= 0.4.3),
    ggplot2 (>= 2.0.0),
    grid (>= 3.2.3),
    gtable (>= 0.1.2),
    magrittr (>= 1.5),
    plyr (>= 1.8.3),
    scales (>= 0.3.0),
Suggests:
    gridExtra (>= 2.0.0),
    knitr (>= 1.11),
    pander (>= 0.6.0),
    testthat (>= 0.11.0),
    RColorBrewer
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
